      "id": "PopularPost153439",
      "post_content": "Once had it in a deck with [quicksilver dagger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=quicksilver dagger). Tap: ping and draw a card. Drawn a [twiddle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=twiddle)? Play it. Before it resolves, the dwarves untap again, ping, draw a card. Twiddle resolves, untaps the dwarves, they ping, you draw a card. Got an [opt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=opt) or [ponder](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=ponder)? And so on... Note that they also trigger off artifacts.",
      "posted_by": "majinara",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost153439\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Once had it in a deck with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"quicksilver dagger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=quicksilver dagger\">quicksilver dagger</a>. Tap: ping and draw a card. Drawn a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"twiddle\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=twiddle\">twiddle</a>? Play it. Before it resolves, the dwarves untap again, ping, draw a card. Twiddle resolves, untaps the dwarves, they ping, you draw a card. Got an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"opt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=opt\">opt</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"ponder\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=ponder\">ponder</a>? And so on... Note that they also trigger off artifacts.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '153439'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy555\">majinara</span>\r\n                                (4/21/2011 11:46:11 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_Main